# Default Test Host

When running functional tests, manual script validation, or any ad-hoc testing that requires a remote host:

- **Default host**: `conno.example.com`
- Connect via: `ssh -F ~/.aba/ssh.conf conno.example.com`
- This host has sudo access, dnsmasq available, chrony installed
- Use this unless the user specifies a different host
